1
00:00:10,460 --> 00:00:12,230
You are too harsh on me.

2
00:00:14,131 --> 00:00:16,130
Can't you just hug me once?

3
00:00:37,320 --> 00:00:39,020
Be born again.

4
00:00:41,091 --> 00:00:42,660
I will wait.

5
00:01:32,309 --> 00:01:35,280
(Hae Ra)

6
00:01:38,949 --> 00:01:40,550
(Hae Ra)

7
00:02:05,509 --> 00:02:08,140
Your call has been forwarded to...

8
00:02:08,145 --> 00:02:10,440
Wine was like a pie in the sky.

9
00:02:10,447 --> 00:02:11,480
This time, the chief director...

10
00:02:11,481 --> 00:02:12,810
Why isn't he picking up?

11
00:02:12,816 --> 00:02:14,680
- I'm tired. - Gosh.

12
00:02:14,985 --> 00:02:16,820
But I'm not drunk.

13
00:02:25,095 --> 00:02:26,360
Hae Ra.

14
00:02:30,867 --> 00:02:32,400
(Episode 17)

15
00:02:32,702 --> 00:02:35,640
Full moon.

16
00:02:36,473 --> 00:02:39,170
When the moon is full.

17
00:02:40,710 --> 00:02:43,310
When the moon is full.

18
00:02:48,251 --> 00:02:50,720
What is she trying to say?

19
00:02:58,028 --> 00:02:59,960
I know.

20
00:03:00,931 --> 00:03:03,060
If the ring receives 
a ray of full moon beam,

21
00:03:03,066 --> 00:03:05,670
it gains strength to grant your wish.

22
00:03:07,904 --> 00:03:11,010
Boon Yi, what would you like to wish?

23
00:03:14,511 --> 00:03:15,710
Secret.

24
00:03:19,549 --> 00:03:21,850
It is cold. Let us go inside.

25
00:03:21,851 --> 00:03:23,520
Tell me when we go inside.

26
00:03:28,291 --> 00:03:30,690
What is your wish? Let me hear it.

27
00:03:35,532 --> 00:03:36,930
My wish is that...

28
00:03:38,535 --> 00:03:41,640
you would not receive poison as punishment.

29
00:03:45,842 --> 00:03:47,880
That is a difficult wish to come true.

30
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:52,550
I asked that...

31
00:03:54,251 --> 00:03:56,580
you would not die...

32
00:03:57,420 --> 00:03:58,990
even if you drank the poison.

33
00:04:06,896 --> 00:04:08,500
Even if you drink the poison...

34
00:04:09,866 --> 00:04:12,970
Whatever comes your way...

35
00:04:16,606 --> 00:04:18,110
I asked that...

36
00:04:18,541 --> 00:04:21,980
you never let go of your life...

37
00:04:22,679 --> 00:04:24,110
easily.

38
00:04:30,820 --> 00:04:32,190
You wished upon that ring.

39
00:04:36,559 --> 00:04:38,330
Okay. Boon Yi.

40
00:04:38,995 --> 00:04:40,800
I will wear that ring...

41
00:04:41,298 --> 00:04:43,100
when I receive poison.

42
00:04:46,236 --> 00:04:47,840
Which finger would fit?

43
00:04:51,975 --> 00:04:54,680
I do not like jokes.

44
00:04:54,844 --> 00:04:56,310
I am not joking.

45
00:04:56,346 --> 00:04:58,750
You made an earnest wish upon that ring.

46
00:04:59,049 --> 00:05:01,280
So it should be in contact with my skin.

47
00:05:01,284 --> 00:05:04,350
I will put it in my inside pocket at least,

48
00:05:04,921 --> 00:05:06,590
so I would never die.

49
00:05:08,658 --> 00:05:11,530
Please do not die.

50
00:05:12,095 --> 00:05:13,530
I will not die.

51
00:05:14,664 --> 00:05:15,900
Never.

52
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,300
Not ever.

53
00:05:36,353 --> 00:05:37,850
I will not die.

54
00:05:38,922 --> 00:05:40,220
Never.

55
00:05:42,425 --> 00:05:43,560
Not ever.

56
00:05:54,371 --> 00:05:56,810
Die in there!

57
00:05:58,475 --> 00:06:00,910
Melt this ring, and make a new blade for this.

58
00:06:01,678 --> 00:06:04,180
On the tiger's month, day, and hour,

59
00:06:05,415 --> 00:06:08,550
make a knife that is extremely hard and sharp.

60
00:06:50,794 --> 00:06:52,060
What is this?

61
00:06:56,433 --> 00:06:57,800
What is this dress?

62
00:06:59,736 --> 00:07:01,100
Answer me!

63
00:07:02,672 --> 00:07:03,970
Baek Hee.

64
00:07:05,742 --> 00:07:07,480
We have to leave.

65
00:07:11,181 --> 00:07:12,350
I...

66
00:07:15,285 --> 00:07:17,350
killed him.

67
00:07:55,658 --> 00:07:59,160
Soo Ho. Wake up.

68
00:07:59,295 --> 00:08:01,660
Open your eyes, Soo Ho.

69
00:08:17,981 --> 00:08:19,980
Soo Ho.

70
00:08:19,983 --> 00:08:22,680
No. You can't die.

71
00:08:51,214 --> 00:08:54,050
Soo Ho.

72
00:08:58,021 --> 00:08:59,420
Please come back.

73
00:09:00,523 --> 00:09:03,590
Please make him come back.

74
00:09:04,861 --> 00:09:07,660
Please save him.

75
00:09:09,098 --> 00:09:11,500
Sharon. I brought stuff from Dongdaemun.

76
00:09:11,501 --> 00:09:12,800
They're...

77
00:09:19,609 --> 00:09:20,810
What happened...

78
00:09:21,444 --> 00:09:22,710
to Mr. Moon?

79
00:09:23,079 --> 00:09:24,450
Call an ambulance.

80
00:09:27,584 --> 00:09:30,080
That's Sharon's.

81
00:09:30,086 --> 00:09:31,790
I said call an ambulance!

82
00:09:32,455 --> 00:09:34,660
Sharon.

83
00:09:35,825 --> 00:09:38,660
Sharon. Where are you?

84
00:09:39,262 --> 00:09:41,930
- Sharon. Where are you? - Wake up.

85
00:09:42,365 --> 00:09:43,900
Please come back.

86
00:09:45,702 --> 00:09:48,170
Please let him live.

87
00:10:11,494 --> 00:10:12,960
Charge 200.

88
00:10:13,563 --> 00:10:14,700
Clear!

89
00:10:46,596 --> 00:10:47,800
Mr. Jung.

90
00:10:53,436 --> 00:10:54,500
Soo Ho.

91
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:05,480
It's been so long.

92
00:11:05,481 --> 00:11:06,550
Soo Ho.

93
00:11:07,350 --> 00:11:09,020
You've become a decent, young man.

94
00:11:11,854 --> 00:11:14,560
I had so much to talk to you when I met you.

95
00:11:16,959 --> 00:11:18,060
I'm sorry,

96
00:11:18,661 --> 00:11:19,890
and thank you.

97
00:11:23,633 --> 00:11:25,630
Hae Ra and I are getting married.

98
00:11:26,102 --> 00:11:27,270
Soo Ho.

99
00:11:27,870 --> 00:11:28,940
Yes?

100
00:11:29,972 --> 00:11:31,140
You...

101
00:11:31,541 --> 00:11:34,010
shouldn't be here. Go back.

102
00:11:37,447 --> 00:11:39,180
Did you forget your promise with Hae Ra?

103
00:11:43,486 --> 00:11:44,690
Soo Ho.

104
00:11:45,254 --> 00:11:46,590
Soo Ho.

105
00:12:01,571 --> 00:12:02,900
Soo Ho...

106
00:12:13,249 --> 00:12:14,550
His pulse is stable,

107
00:12:14,550 --> 00:12:16,380
so he'll regain his consciousness soon.

108
00:12:16,586 --> 00:12:17,820
Let's wait and see.

109
00:12:19,222 --> 00:12:21,660
His heart stopped due to excessive bleeding?

110
00:12:22,325 --> 00:12:23,390
Yes.

111
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:26,160
Strangely, he didn't have any external injury...

112
00:12:26,162 --> 00:12:27,930
that could've caused excessive bleeding.

113
00:12:28,865 --> 00:12:31,300
We did a checkup on him to see if it was a stroke,

114
00:12:31,300 --> 00:12:32,670
but it wasn't.

115
00:12:33,302 --> 00:12:35,270
We've never had such a case before.

116
00:12:35,705 --> 00:12:38,310
So we need to wait and see his condition first.

117
00:12:44,280 --> 00:12:45,680
What happened?

118
00:12:46,349 --> 00:12:48,180
Are you the one who called the ambulance?

119
00:12:50,119 --> 00:12:52,090
Where was he?

120
00:12:52,221 --> 00:12:54,920
Let's talk outside.

121
00:12:57,760 --> 00:12:59,460
At Sharon Tailor?

122
00:13:00,696 --> 00:13:03,130
I think he came to try on his wedding suit.

123
00:13:04,333 --> 00:13:05,560
What do you mean?

124
00:13:05,568 --> 00:13:07,200
We're supposed to make...

125
00:13:07,203 --> 00:13:10,040
a dress and a suit for your wedding.

126
00:13:10,273 --> 00:13:11,410
What?

127
00:13:12,742 --> 00:13:14,780
You didn't get any call from Sharon, did you?

128
00:13:15,745 --> 00:13:17,380
Don't meet her even if she does.

129
00:13:23,953 --> 00:13:25,480
When did he ask you...

130
00:13:25,488 --> 00:13:26,620
to make them?

131
00:13:26,622 --> 00:13:29,860
Mr. Moon didn't ask it himself.

132
00:13:30,126 --> 00:13:31,530
Then who...

133
00:13:32,695 --> 00:13:34,930
It was Baek Hee.

134
00:13:35,631 --> 00:13:38,170
That was why Mr. Moon said he'd wear it.

135
00:13:41,571 --> 00:13:43,540
Why did she ask such a favor?

136
00:13:43,739 --> 00:13:44,940
I don't know.

137
00:13:47,343 --> 00:13:48,540
And...

138
00:13:48,978 --> 00:13:52,380
I really don't want to say this...

139
00:13:56,652 --> 00:13:59,390
I saw Sharon's silver knife...

140
00:14:00,122 --> 00:14:03,290
dropped next to Mr. Moon.

141
00:14:04,861 --> 00:14:06,890
I didn't see it in the ambulance.

142
00:14:07,096 --> 00:14:08,900
When he was down unconscious,

143
00:14:09,599 --> 00:14:12,500
Baek Hee was with him.

144
00:14:17,540 --> 00:14:19,110
Where's she now?

145
00:14:31,020 --> 00:14:32,250
Get changed.

146
00:14:32,255 --> 00:14:33,590
I don't want to see you in that.

147
00:14:36,192 --> 00:14:38,030
Are the police looking for me...

148
00:14:39,495 --> 00:14:40,930
to arrest me as a murder suspect?

149
00:14:41,264 --> 00:14:43,700
He fortunately saved his life.

150
00:14:54,243 --> 00:14:55,580
He's alive?

151
00:15:01,751 --> 00:15:02,950
I am...

152
00:15:05,121 --> 00:15:06,920
giving up on you.

153
00:15:12,495 --> 00:15:14,530
I don't want to see you anymore.

154
00:15:16,365 --> 00:15:17,530
Baek Hee.

155
00:15:19,902 --> 00:15:21,440
Leave this country.

156
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:27,140
Don't think about showing yourself before the two.

157
00:15:29,812 --> 00:15:31,780
Don't you think you're too harsh on me?

158
00:15:32,248 --> 00:15:33,910
Shall I report you to the police...

159
00:15:34,850 --> 00:15:36,880
that a 200-year-old monster...

160
00:15:36,886 --> 00:15:38,790
tried to hurt a person?

161
00:15:39,522 --> 00:15:41,790
You made me this way.

162
00:15:41,991 --> 00:15:43,090
Yes.

163
00:15:45,227 --> 00:15:47,160
Just kill me instead, Sharon.

164
00:15:47,997 --> 00:15:49,930
And have your revenge.

165
00:16:12,621 --> 00:16:13,920
What happened?

166
00:16:13,923 --> 00:16:15,720
Tell me in detail.

167
00:16:15,725 --> 00:16:17,290
He's a bit hurt.

168
00:16:17,393 --> 00:16:19,760
Don't worry too much. I think he'll recover soon.

169
00:16:19,762 --> 00:16:22,430
Where did he get hurt that he's in the hospital?

170
00:16:22,431 --> 00:16:23,800
He got into a car accident?

171
00:16:24,500 --> 00:16:26,670
He sort of overworked.

172
00:16:27,136 --> 00:16:28,700
He'll recover soon.

173
00:16:28,704 --> 00:16:31,040
Did you call his employees?

174
00:16:31,040 --> 00:16:32,110
Not yet.

175
00:16:33,042 --> 00:16:35,080
I'll go nurse him from tomorrow morning.

176
00:16:36,479 --> 00:16:37,580
I'll call you later.

177
00:16:39,882 --> 00:16:43,280
Goodness, what's going on?

178
00:16:43,352 --> 00:16:47,090
He went to work with a smile on his face earlier.

179
00:16:48,357 --> 00:16:49,460
(Sharon Tailor)

180
00:16:51,727 --> 00:16:52,890
Hello?

181
00:16:53,496 --> 00:16:56,060
Yes, you heard the news.

182
00:16:56,632 --> 00:16:58,070
Right.

183
00:16:58,300 --> 00:17:00,370
He's in Haneul Hospital.

184
00:17:04,206 --> 00:17:05,340
It's okay.

185
00:17:06,909 --> 00:17:08,440
Don't mind me,

186
00:17:08,611 --> 00:17:10,180
and take your time, Hae Ra.

187
00:17:10,913 --> 00:17:12,550
I'm not hungry.

188
00:17:35,471 --> 00:17:37,970
I think he's reacting to sounds.

189
00:17:39,241 --> 00:17:41,780
I told you he'll regain his consciousness soon.

190
00:17:43,813 --> 00:17:45,380
I'll check his condition,

191
00:17:45,381 --> 00:17:47,450
so you may stay outside for a bit.

192
00:17:47,917 --> 00:17:50,780
His guardian will arrive soon.

193
00:17:52,021 --> 00:17:53,090
Well, then.

194
00:18:02,965 --> 00:18:04,230
Mr. Moon Soo Ho.

195
00:18:04,834 --> 00:18:06,230
Do you hear me?

196
00:18:07,870 --> 00:18:10,000
Move your fingers again.

197
00:18:12,775 --> 00:18:14,040
Good.

198
00:18:15,744 --> 00:18:17,510
Open your eyes.

199
00:18:56,552 --> 00:18:58,190
(Dr. Park Ji Yeon)

200
00:19:33,155 --> 00:19:35,260
I told you to be born again.

201
00:20:27,142 --> 00:20:28,210
Soo Ho.

202
00:20:32,748 --> 00:20:34,150
Are you awake?

203
00:20:35,384 --> 00:20:36,750
Where am I?

204
00:20:37,753 --> 00:20:39,290
You're in the hospital.

205
00:21:01,310 --> 00:21:05,550
(Haneul Hospital)

206
00:21:08,651 --> 00:21:10,820
Don't worry about me, and get to work.

207
00:21:11,654 --> 00:21:13,980
Do you feel pain, or does it ache anywhere?

208
00:21:13,989 --> 00:21:15,220
Not at all.

209
00:21:15,224 --> 00:21:16,860
I feel much better than usual.

210
00:21:18,927 --> 00:21:21,230
Do you not remember why you came here?

211
00:21:23,565 --> 00:21:24,700
I suddenly felt dizzy...

212
00:21:24,700 --> 00:21:26,870
and feverish, so I came to the emergency room.

213
00:21:28,871 --> 00:21:30,000
Yesterday,

214
00:21:30,873 --> 00:21:32,270
it was odd that there was no wound...

215
00:21:32,274 --> 00:21:34,210
even though you bled a lot.

216
00:21:34,677 --> 00:21:36,240
I didn't bleed.

217
00:21:36,245 --> 00:21:37,810
I walked in here myself.

218
00:21:39,815 --> 00:21:41,980
Do you know where you left your clothes?

219
00:21:42,918 --> 00:21:44,490
That's what I don't know.

220
00:21:46,255 --> 00:21:47,650
That's odd.

221
00:21:48,290 --> 00:21:49,620
You'll be late. Get to work.

222
00:21:49,625 --> 00:21:51,060
I'll be fine.

223
00:21:51,060 --> 00:21:55,060
The temperature dropped to minus 16.3°C.

224
00:21:55,631 --> 00:21:56,960
I'll call you.

225
00:21:59,001 --> 00:22:01,730
But the wind is less harsh than yesterday.

226
00:22:01,737 --> 00:22:03,970
You can't tell what will happen with the weather.

227
00:22:03,972 --> 00:22:05,110
Bye.

228
00:22:06,041 --> 00:22:08,170
But it will stay pretty cold.

229
00:22:08,177 --> 00:22:11,380
Other areas may drop to minus 8°C.

230
00:22:12,381 --> 00:22:13,550
Soo Ho.

231
00:22:15,918 --> 00:22:17,450
Forgive me.

232
00:22:21,957 --> 00:22:23,390
For you,

233
00:22:25,361 --> 00:22:27,490
Hae Ra, and Sharon,

234
00:22:29,665 --> 00:22:32,070
you must forget about today.

235
00:22:36,872 --> 00:22:39,210
What happened last night?

236
00:22:41,944 --> 00:22:43,240
Next news.

237
00:22:43,245 --> 00:22:45,780
The town that was selected for the city revival...

238
00:22:45,781 --> 00:22:49,750
demands the decision to be cancelled.

239
00:22:49,752 --> 00:22:50,920
For whom...

240
00:22:51,720 --> 00:22:53,920
are we reviving this town for,

241
00:22:53,922 --> 00:22:56,760
and for whom are we preserving this?

242
00:22:57,292 --> 00:23:00,760
The taxpayers' money will be used for this,

243
00:23:00,896 --> 00:23:05,130
and people point out that this profits no one.

244
00:23:05,134 --> 00:23:07,200
Do we have to continue this project?

245
00:23:34,963 --> 00:23:36,760
She's slacking off right after her promotion.

246
00:23:36,765 --> 00:23:37,970
Hae Ra, I mean.

247
00:23:38,167 --> 00:23:39,900
You have to give her a break.

248
00:23:39,902 --> 00:23:42,140
Mr. Moon suddenly got hospitalized.

249
00:23:43,138 --> 00:23:45,710
She did send the proposal late in the night.

250
00:23:45,841 --> 00:23:47,970
She sent an email while she was nursing him.

251
00:23:47,976 --> 00:23:50,210
Really? I'll check.

252
00:23:50,212 --> 00:23:51,650
Oh, right. Sir.

253
00:23:52,181 --> 00:23:54,080
We're going to go...

254
00:23:54,082 --> 00:23:56,120
and visit Mr. Moon during our lunch time.

255
00:23:56,985 --> 00:23:58,220
- I'll let you go. - Okay.

256
00:23:58,220 --> 00:23:59,690
Only if I like your proposal.

257
00:23:59,888 --> 00:24:01,560
- Come on, you... - Understood?

258
00:24:07,830 --> 00:24:09,730
You clearly told me that yesterday.

259
00:24:09,731 --> 00:24:12,300
You saw Sharon's knife, but not in the ambulance.

260
00:24:12,301 --> 00:24:13,430
You said...

261
00:24:13,435 --> 00:24:15,470
Baek Hee was there when Soo Ho collapsed.

262
00:24:15,471 --> 00:24:16,470
I did?

263
00:24:16,472 --> 00:24:18,770
Yes, you did. In front of the emergency room.

264
00:24:18,974 --> 00:24:21,170
When did I say that?

265
00:24:31,887 --> 00:24:34,290
Why do you suddenly need your passport?

266
00:24:37,392 --> 00:24:39,230
Something came up.

267
00:24:41,830 --> 00:24:43,400
Please take care of...

268
00:24:43,632 --> 00:24:46,100
Sharon Tailor while I'm gone.

269
00:24:47,402 --> 00:24:49,170
You're the owner...

270
00:24:49,171 --> 00:24:50,540
and the chief designer for a while.

271
00:24:52,374 --> 00:24:54,810
How long will you be gone for?

272
00:24:56,812 --> 00:24:57,980
I don't know.

273
00:25:00,315 --> 00:25:01,920
And what happened yesterday?

274
00:25:04,553 --> 00:25:07,120
Why was your knife...

275
00:25:07,523 --> 00:25:10,060
on the floor next to Mr. Moon?

276
00:25:12,494 --> 00:25:14,390
What happened?

277
00:25:19,234 --> 00:25:20,570
Seung Goo.

278
00:25:22,938 --> 00:25:24,140
Come here.

279
00:25:24,640 --> 00:25:26,610
Let me give you a bottle of perfume as a gift.

280
00:25:41,323 --> 00:25:42,690
Yesterday,

281
00:25:43,659 --> 00:25:46,290
nothing happened, Seung Goo.

282
00:25:48,430 --> 00:25:49,900
Nothing.

283
00:25:54,903 --> 00:25:57,000
Then why were you at the hospital?

284
00:25:57,940 --> 00:26:00,240
Yesterday? I was there because my stomach...

285
00:26:00,242 --> 00:26:02,210
suddenly got upset, and I saw you there.

