It's surprising...

569
00:47:15,983 --> 00:47:18,020
that your story was found in the grave.

570
00:47:19,520 --> 00:47:21,490
But I don't believe in a past life.

571
00:47:24,158 --> 00:47:26,160
It doesn't matter even if you don't believe it.

572
00:47:26,794 --> 00:47:29,800
But it's true that such things happened...

573
00:47:30,231 --> 00:47:31,560
in the past.

574
00:47:34,768 --> 00:47:37,070
If your story is all true,

575
00:47:39,273 --> 00:47:42,310
and Choi Seo Rin is an immortal being,

576
00:47:44,645 --> 00:47:46,450
then she'll appear again.

577
00:47:48,415 --> 00:47:49,920
Maybe when you two...

578
00:47:51,051 --> 00:47:53,690
become a happy old couple.

579
00:47:54,755 --> 00:47:57,420
If she appears before my eyes again,

580
00:47:59,393 --> 00:48:02,360
I think I'll be able to believe in all this story.

581
00:48:04,298 --> 00:48:07,300
When you're upset or confused,

582
00:48:07,768 --> 00:48:09,570
tell me anytime.

583
00:48:12,573 --> 00:48:14,170
Is Sharon Tailor...

584
00:48:15,042 --> 00:48:16,780
still closed?

585
00:48:17,678 --> 00:48:20,050
Seung Goo is working hard to run it.

586
00:48:20,414 --> 00:48:21,980
Pay a visit some time,

587
00:48:21,982 --> 00:48:23,620
and keep him company.

588
00:48:24,418 --> 00:48:25,820
He must be lonely.

589
00:48:27,821 --> 00:48:30,560
Okay, I'll visit there one day.

590
00:49:28,449 --> 00:49:30,020
Stop it.

591
00:50:32,579 --> 00:50:34,050
Did you talk with her all right?

592
00:50:34,381 --> 00:50:35,550
Yes.

593
00:50:35,983 --> 00:50:37,150
But...

594
00:50:37,951 --> 00:50:39,590
I don't believe in the old story.

595
00:50:40,454 --> 00:50:41,650
Then don't.

596
00:50:42,322 --> 00:50:43,460
But...

597
00:50:44,792 --> 00:50:47,330
I think it's true that we're meant to be.

598
00:50:49,663 --> 00:50:50,730
Hae Ra.

599
00:50:51,398 --> 00:50:52,970
Do you know what my dream is?

600
00:50:53,434 --> 00:50:54,570
What is it?

601
00:51:00,040 --> 00:51:02,010
To grow old with you like them.

602
00:51:04,478 --> 00:51:05,640
Is that all?

603
00:51:07,247 --> 00:51:08,410
That's all.

604
00:51:12,252 --> 00:51:13,390
That's very simple.

605
00:51:15,756 --> 00:51:17,290
Let's make our wedding pictures...

606
00:51:17,891 --> 00:51:19,830
look really great and wonderful.

607
00:51:20,260 --> 00:51:21,330
Okay.

608
00:51:22,429 --> 00:51:25,460
Let's live a happy and healthy life.

609
00:51:27,968 --> 00:51:29,070
Let us do that.

610
00:51:42,282 --> 00:51:43,650
Hey, stop the car.

611
00:51:47,821 --> 00:51:49,490
- Did you see that? - What?

612
00:51:51,758 --> 00:51:53,330
This is Lee Hyun Sik of patrol car three.

613
00:51:53,560 --> 00:51:55,220
Was there any other suicide report?

614
00:51:55,229 --> 00:51:57,860
None. There has been no other suicide today.

615
00:51:59,433 --> 00:52:00,670
That's odd.

616
00:52:00,801 --> 00:52:01,970
What is it?

617
00:52:03,003 --> 00:52:05,700
I just saw a woman's head right above the water.

618
00:52:05,706 --> 00:52:07,100
What are you talking about?

619
00:52:07,107 --> 00:52:09,170
Han River is completely frozen today.

620
00:52:10,811 --> 00:52:11,880
Let's go.

621
00:52:12,012 --> 00:52:13,080
Okay.

622
00:52:41,542 --> 00:52:42,670
Hey, Sharon!

623
00:52:55,322 --> 00:52:57,920
I got confused for a second.

624
00:53:00,861 --> 00:53:02,490
You must miss her a lot.

625
00:53:03,030 --> 00:53:04,800
No, I don't.

626
00:53:06,900 --> 00:53:10,070
I was going to brag about my new design.

627
00:53:10,504 --> 00:53:11,770
Seung Goo.

628
00:53:12,673 --> 00:53:14,270
For the next 30 years,

629
00:53:15,642 --> 00:53:17,780
no, maybe 50 years,

630
00:53:20,414 --> 00:53:23,520
can you keep this place as good as today?

631
00:53:24,184 --> 00:53:25,680
Is Sharon...

632
00:53:26,420 --> 00:53:28,020
gone for good?

633
00:53:28,755 --> 00:53:30,060
I don't know either.

634
00:53:33,794 --> 00:53:35,390
No.

635
00:53:36,830 --> 00:53:38,360
I don't think I can.

636
00:53:41,201 --> 00:53:43,040
If she doesn't come back,

637
00:53:43,370 --> 00:53:46,170
I'm going to ruin this place and sell it off.

638
00:54:01,822 --> 00:54:02,950
Sharon.

639
00:54:05,726 --> 00:54:06,860
I guess...

640
00:54:08,962 --> 00:54:11,900
there is someone that misses you.

641
00:54:14,901 --> 00:54:16,070
Father.

642
00:54:16,370 --> 00:54:17,540
Mother.

643
00:54:18,272 --> 00:54:21,040
I am here. It is me, Seo Rin.

644
00:54:21,975 --> 00:54:23,580
Please come out.

645
00:54:25,279 --> 00:54:27,050
I am here.

646
00:54:27,314 --> 00:54:28,410
Yes.

647
00:54:28,649 --> 00:54:29,950
Father.

648
00:54:29,950 --> 00:54:32,780
There used to be people that loved you.

649
00:54:38,759 --> 00:54:40,590
Once you graduate from dressmaking school,

650
00:54:40,861 --> 00:54:42,730
let's return to Joseon.

651
00:54:43,664 --> 00:54:45,930
I'm sure everyone who remembers us...

652
00:54:45,932 --> 00:54:48,230
are all long gone.

653
00:54:48,302 --> 00:54:50,270
How long do you think we'll live like this?

654
00:54:50,771 --> 00:54:52,840
One day, when you meet Boon Yi,

655
00:54:53,440 --> 00:54:54,910
make her some clothes.

656
00:54:55,142 --> 00:54:57,110
Can people really be born again?

657
00:54:58,578 --> 00:55:00,250
People who lived a great life...

658
00:55:00,947 --> 00:55:02,650
or a very wicked life...

659
00:55:03,150 --> 00:55:04,580
probably don't.

660
00:55:05,519 --> 00:55:06,720
But...

661
00:55:07,254 --> 00:55:08,850
those who left...

662
00:55:08,855 --> 00:55:10,920
with great sorrow and regret...

663
00:55:10,991 --> 00:55:12,260
may get...

664
00:55:12,693 --> 00:55:14,930
one more chance by fate.

665
00:55:15,862 --> 00:55:17,300
How do you know?

666
00:55:17,931 --> 00:55:19,300
If not, then never mind.

667
00:55:20,334 --> 00:55:21,930
I don't want to make any clothes.

668
00:55:22,469 --> 00:55:24,300
The only two things you are good at are...

669
00:55:24,371 --> 00:55:25,730
making yourself look pretty...

670
00:55:25,739 --> 00:55:27,810
and getting jealous.

671
00:55:27,941 --> 00:55:29,540
Make use of that.

672
00:55:30,744 --> 00:55:32,280
Let's go play mah-jong.

673
00:55:32,879 --> 00:55:34,080
Go study.

674
00:55:34,081 --> 00:55:36,620
It's just for today.

675
00:55:38,185 --> 00:55:39,380
Let's go.

676
00:55:46,126 --> 00:55:48,290
I don't know where you are,

677
00:55:50,731 --> 00:55:53,200
but atone for everything you did there,

678
00:55:56,203 --> 00:55:58,300
and never return.

679
00:56:02,142 --> 00:56:03,580
Baek Hee.

680
00:56:19,793 --> 00:56:21,130
Can you get some forks?

681
00:56:28,001 --> 00:56:31,200
Did you two hold a photo exhibit yesterday?

682
00:56:31,471 --> 00:56:33,140
I put them up. I'll take them down.

683
00:56:33,140 --> 00:56:34,640
They look great. Leave them up.

684
00:56:34,641 --> 00:56:36,070
Don't take them down.

685
00:56:36,143 --> 00:56:38,010
Are you going to the construction site later?

686
00:56:38,011 --> 00:56:39,470
Yes, after I stop by my office.

687
00:56:39,479 --> 00:56:41,810
Then can you drop me off at the subway station?

688
00:56:42,182 --> 00:56:43,520
It's the weekend. Do you want to come?

689
00:56:43,683 --> 00:56:44,750
Should I?

690
00:56:44,851 --> 00:56:46,320
I'll call you later.

691
00:56:46,953 --> 00:56:48,190
Do you want some milk?

692
00:57:29,029 --> 00:57:30,130
What was that?

693
00:57:31,231 --> 00:57:33,300
Are the lights changing just for you?

694
00:57:33,400 --> 00:57:34,470
What?

695
00:57:34,835 --> 00:57:36,670
I guess so.

696
00:58:05,232 --> 00:58:07,730
Sharon will be surprised to see this.

697
00:58:09,402 --> 00:58:10,740
I have a feeling...

698
00:58:11,037 --> 00:58:13,240
that she will come back in May.

699
00:58:14,741 --> 00:58:16,310
She likes roses.

700
00:58:23,083 --> 00:58:26,420
Who is it?

701
00:58:30,123 --> 00:58:31,520
Hae Ra.

702
00:58:34,794 --> 00:58:36,560
Goodness, you're so awful.

703
00:58:36,563 --> 00:58:38,160
I haven't seen you in ages.

704
00:58:38,565 --> 00:58:40,100
I'll visit from time to time.

705
00:58:41,268 --> 00:58:42,930
Everything looks the same.

706
00:58:42,969 --> 00:58:44,740
I'm going to leave it as it is...

707
00:58:44,838 --> 00:58:46,340
until Sharon returns.

708
00:58:46,373 --> 00:58:48,210
When will she come back?

709
00:58:48,508 --> 00:58:49,770
Baek Hee said...

710
00:58:50,043 --> 00:58:52,840
she'll be back in 30 or 50 years.

711
00:58:53,313 --> 00:58:54,410
But who knows?

712
00:58:56,650 --> 00:58:58,480
I came to return this.

713
00:59:03,523 --> 00:59:04,620
What?

714
00:59:14,067 --> 00:59:15,500
After I put this on,

715
00:59:16,002 --> 00:59:18,200
I went through a series of odd events.

716
00:59:21,241 --> 00:59:23,210
It was a turning point in my life.

717
00:59:23,510 --> 00:59:25,540
Anyway, I became happy.

718
00:59:25,612 --> 00:59:27,050
This is a very special coat,

719
00:59:27,547 --> 00:59:28,950
so I want to return it.

720
00:59:28,982 --> 00:59:30,150
Really?

721
00:59:30,850 --> 00:59:32,280
Did your life change...

722
00:59:32,352 --> 00:59:34,320
after you put this on?

723
00:59:34,521 --> 00:59:35,590
Yes.

724
00:59:39,392 --> 00:59:41,090
I'm thankful for the coat,

725
00:59:42,629 --> 00:59:44,300
but I'm also scared of it.

726
01:00:28,775 --> 01:00:30,440
Yes, dark brown.

727
01:00:31,111 --> 01:00:33,380
Seung Goo, I'm leaving.

728
01:00:34,180 --> 01:00:35,310
One second.

729
01:00:35,649 --> 01:00:37,150
Have a cup of tea before you leave.

730
01:00:38,451 --> 01:00:39,950
Then I'll tell Soo Ho to come here.

731
01:00:39,953 --> 01:00:41,590
We have to be somewhere later.

732
01:00:41,755 --> 01:00:43,190
That'd be wonderful.

733
01:00:44,157 --> 01:00:46,690
Yes. Hello? Yes.

734
01:01:10,750 --> 01:01:13,420
Who are you?

735
01:02:02,068 --> 01:02:04,440
(Black Knight - The Man Who Guards Me)

736
01:02:04,504 --> 01:02:06,370
I think she's pretending not to know me.

737
01:02:06,372 --> 01:02:07,770
I came back very soon this time, right?

738
01:02:07,774 --> 01:02:08,900
You don't remember?

739
01:02:08,908 --> 01:02:10,370
The chic Sharon style.

740
01:02:10,376 --> 01:02:11,710
She's back.

741
01:02:11,711 --> 01:02:13,240
I'm marrying Soo Ho.

742
01:02:13,313 --> 01:02:15,080
My employees prepared this.

743
01:02:15,081 --> 01:02:16,340
How about champagne?

744
01:02:16,349 --> 01:02:19,420
Let's stop. Please!

745
01:02:19,586 --> 01:02:21,520
I'm a son of a criminal.

746
01:02:21,521 --> 01:02:23,520
Hae Ra said she'd work...

747
01:02:23,523 --> 01:02:25,620
in the office in Rome for two years.

748
01:02:25,625 --> 01:02:27,360
I don't want you to go.

749
01:02:27,360 --> 01:02:29,090
All I need is you.

750
01:02:29,395 --> 01:02:30,860
This isn't a dream, is it?

